{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"455","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"氣候風險管理 永續資訊新趨勢","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'>04:10<span style='margin: 0px;'>&nbsp; </span>2019/05/08</span><span lang='EN-US' style='background: white; margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 1pt;'>&nbsp;</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'> </span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'> </span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 51, 136); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'><a href='https://www.chinatimes.com/reporter/1056'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 51, 136); font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; text-decoration: none;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px;'>呂淑美</span></span></a></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>證交所</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>7</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>日與氣候變遷相關財務揭露工作小組、台灣永續能源研究基金會、高齊能源科技及安本標準投資管理共同舉辦「氣候相關財務揭露推廣論壇」及「</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>ESG</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>投資論壇」。證交所總經理簡立忠致詞時指出，氣候變遷相關資訊揭露，已逐漸成為永續資訊揭露的新趨勢。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>簡立忠表示，隨著國際間主要永續評比機構皆將氣候相關財務揭露專案小組（</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>TCFD</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>）所提建議納入報導、評比問卷架構中，證交所亦強化上市公司非財務資訊揭露，規定強制編制</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>CSR</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>報告書的上市公司，自</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2019</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年起發布之報告書必須依照</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>GRI</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>準則編製報告書。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>簡立忠說，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>GRI</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>準則中「</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>201</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>經濟績效」亦明確要求企業揭露氣候變遷所產生的財務影響及其風險與機會，公司治理評鑑亦將「公司是否制定節能減碳、溫室氣體減量、減少用水或其他廢棄物管理政策」納入評鑑指標中。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>TCFD</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>秘書處代表</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>Curtis Ravenel</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>分享國際間面對氣候變遷之挑戰，為提升企業資訊透明度，國際金融穩定委員會（</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>FSB</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>）於</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2017</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>6</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>月正式發布氣候相關財務揭露建議，要求企業依照建議之架構：治理、策略、風險管理及指標和目標，了解氣候變遷可能對營運造成的財務影響，並提供利害關係人相關且可靠的財務衡量資訊，</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>TCFD</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>透過彈性化的建議指引，引導國際間企業重視氣候風險之管理。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>台灣永續能源研究基金會董事長簡又新指出，企業永續報告書的數量依國內報告書平台統計從</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2008</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年的</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>10</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>餘家，成長到</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2018</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>528</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>家，有突破性成長，「</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>TCSA</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>台灣企業永續獎」歷屆參獎企業成長至</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>236</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>家，參獎企業總營業額與</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>2017</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>年</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>GDP</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>比值約為</span><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>82</span><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>％。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:15.0pt;margin-left:&#10;0cm;background:white'><span style='margin: 0px; color: black; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;'>證交所公司治理部副理余宗普分享我國機構投資人在履行盡職治理相關推動實務，隨著機構投資人占我國交易市場交易比重逐步攀升，越來越多機構投資人簽署盡職治理守則，並透過出席股東會、行使投票權、適當與被投資公司之經營階層對話與互動等方式參與公司治理。</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px;'><span style='margin: 0px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;'><a href='https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20190508000401-260206?chdtv'><font color='#0000ff'>https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20190508000401-260206?chdtv</font></a></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-05-09","clk_count":"229"}},"__N_SSG":true}